Pacifix was now riding along the ridge in the ocean, connecting the
island they were on to the main continent, flushing through the rock and
coral formations, trying not to dammage any if possible. "Fascinating.
Of course being Autobots, we know exactly how important the Matrix is,
as it is the corner stone of our society. But tell me, you must have
some kind of connection with ancient Autobots to be so close to the
matrix."
